Quickstrike:







Quickstrike chuckled lightly and weakly to himself. He knew they had lost 
the ownership of the Predacons ship, but Hell Beast's troops were the ones 
loosing. They now had a ship and computer with them that wouldn't listen to 
their commands. It was a dead ship. When ever they'll get the auto-guns 
brought back on-line, the ship will turn on them. She still had the 
programing he gave Her earlier. The fools. And they would never get Her back 
the way she was without him. They would never guess he was he one that did 
all this. And he would never crack.
